column2: SELECT  b.*,a.ra as sdss_ra, a.dec as sdss_dec, a.z as sdss_z,a.snMedian_r as sdss_sn_r, a.plate as sdss_plate, a.mjd as sdss_mjd, a.fiberID as sdss_fiberID into mydb.nocross_galpair_B1#_sdss_dr1#new2_# from  mydb.nocross_galpair_B1#_sdss_dr1#new2 as b   CROSS APPLY  dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(b.ra_B,b.dec_B,#) as c   join DR1#.specObjAll as a on a.bestObjID=c.ObjID
